0.1.1.name: wordpress/serverbuddy-by-pluginbuddy
0.1.1.description: ServerBuddy by PluginBuddy.com tests server configuration to look for problems with hosting configuration and determine hosting quality. Additionally it provides several tools such a WordPress CRON viewer, site size mapper, database table viewer, and more.
